'''都会公园站''' （{{lang-en|Metropark Station}}）是美国[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[密德薩克斯郡_(紐澤西州)|密德薩克斯郡]]{{link-en|艾斯林 (新泽西州)|Iselin, New Jersey|艾斯林}}的多式联运枢纽车站，距离[[纽约宾州车站|纽约宾州车站]]西南24.6英里。本站由[[新泽西交通|新泽西交通]]（NJ Transit）拥有并营运，有美铁列车和[[新泽西通勤铁路|新泽西通勤铁路]][[东北走廊线|东北走廊线]]停靠，新泽西交通还会在高峰期根据铁路时刻运营本站的接驳巴士。

本站位于{{link-en|新泽西州27号公路|New Jersey Route 27}}和{{link-en|花园州收费高速公路|Garden State Parkway}}131号和132号出口附近<ref name="NJDOTMidsex">{{cite web  |title = NJDOT Graphic Information System Maps Middlesex |publisher = New Jersey Department of Transportation|url = https://www.state.nj.us/transportation/gis/maps/middlesex.pdf |accessdate = March 2, 2020}}</ref><ref name=exit_opens>{{cite web |url=http://www.nj.com/traffic/index.ssf/2015/03/what_exit_parkway_exit_numbers_officially_change_today_as_new_exit_opens.html |title=What exit? New Parkway exit opens today as numbers change on others next week |author=Larry Higgs |date=March 13, 2015 |work= |publisher=NJ Advance Media for NJ.com |accessdate=December 11, 2015}}</ref>，同时附近建有一座全天营运的停车楼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metroparkparking.com/ |title=Metropark Parking |work=Metropark Parking |accessdate=June 28, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080621015058/http://metroparkparking.com/ |archivedate=June 21, 2008 }}</ref><ref>https://www.nexusparkingsystems.com/metropark-parking-facility.html</ref>。

本站于1971年11月4日作为停靠高速铁路列车{{link-en|Metroliner (列车)|Metroliner (train)|Metroliner}}的市郊[[停车换乘|停车换乘]]车站、以“花园州都会公园站”（{{lang-en|Garden State Metropark}}）的名称开通，由新泽西州交通部和[[美国交通部|联邦交通部]]投资建设。

==历史==
[[File:Amtrak_GG1_at_Metropark_station,_January_1976.jpg|thumb]]
都会公园站是1960年代{{link-en|Metroliner (列车)|Metroliner (train)|Metroliner}}上线运营后、东北走廊上以[[政府和社会资本合作|PPP]]方式新增了两个[[停车换乘|停车换乘]]车站之一，另一个为位于[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]的{{link-en|首都环路站|Capital Beltway (Amtrak station)}}。两座车站原先规划名称分别为首都环路都会公园站（{{lang-en|Capital Beltway Metropark}}）和花园州都会公园（{{lang-en|Garden State Metropark}}）站，后简化为现名。根据{{link-en|新泽西州交通部|New Jersey Department of Transportation}}（NJDOT）在1968年底提出的一项计划，该州将为车站的费用出资648,000美元，后调整为140万美元<ref name="pcp021969">{{cite journal | url=http://www.unlikelypcrr.com/page3/Welcome_files/PC_POST_1969-02.pdf | title=Open Line | journal=Penn Central Post | date=February 1969 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006082310/http://www.unlikelypcrr.com/page3/Welcome_files/PC_POST_1969-02.pdf | archivedate=October 6, 2014 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Commuter Rail Station in Jersey to Have Parking for 776 Cars |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1968/12/29/archives/commuter-rail-station-in-jersey-to-have-parking-for-776-cars.html |newspaper=The New York Times |date=December 29, 1968 |page=54 |accessdate=May 30, 2010}}</ref>

[[美铁|美铁]]列车于1971年11月14日起开始停靠本站<ref name="metroparkopens" />。车站最终耗资260万美元，由新泽西交通部和[[美国交通部|联邦交通部]]分担。车站有两座长{{convert|850|ft|adj=on}}的高站台和一个含有820个车位的停车场。为方便停车换乘，车站修建在{{link-en|花园州收费高速公路|Garden State Parkway}}和一个商务园区旁。通勤列车在车站开通初期仍旧使用东侧半英里的艾斯林站<ref name="bt19711106">{{cite news|title=New 'Metropark' in Northern N.J. Timed With Metroliner Extension|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/1098386/metropark_opens|newspaper=[[Bridgeport_Telegram|Bridgeport Telegram]]|date=November 6, 1971|page=29|via = [[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|accessdate =October 2, 2014 }} {{Open access}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=A Park-and-Ride Rail Station Is Dedicated in Jersey |first=Richard |last=Witkin |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1971/11/12/archives/a-parkandride-rail-station-is-dedicated-in-jersey.html |newspaper=The New York Times |date=November 12, 1971 |page=49 |accessdate=May 30, 2010}}</ref>，直至该站于1972年关闭而转而停靠本站{{citation needed|date=October 2014}}。

1979年，车站为纪念新泽西州的民主党联邦参议员{{link-en|哈里森·威廉姆斯|Harrison A. Williams}}在筹建工程中的支持而更名为哈里森·A·威廉姆斯都会公园站（{{lang-en|Harrison A. Williams Metropark Station}}）。然而威廉姆斯于1980年在联邦调查局的{{link-en|Abscam}}行动中陷入贿赂和贪腐丑闻，车站因此取消了其冠名<ref>Bachrach, Judy. [http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20081347,00.html "Facing Expulsion from the Senate He Loves, Harrison Williams Finds Some Unlikely Supporters"], ''[[People_(magazine)|People (magazine)]]'', February 1, 1982. Accessed March 5, 2011. "One of them, who asks for anonymity, recalls 'going over to Pete and Nancy's house in Westfield, N.J. and having coffee together. Pete looked about 80 years old—horrible.'"</ref>。

===翻新===
[[File:NJT_4603_at_Metropark_station,_November_2008.jpg|thumb]]
2007年1月，新泽西交通宣布了耗资3000万美元的车站翻修计划，计划于2010年完成<ref>{{cite news |title=Metropark to Get $30 Million Makeover |first=Kathy |last=Chang |url=http://ems.gmnews.com/news/2007-01-04/Front_Page/034.html |newspaper=Edison-Metuchen Sentinel |date=January 4, 2007 |accessdate=May 30, 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711104028/http://ems.gmnews.com/news/2007-01-04/Front_Page/034.html |archivedate=July 11, 2011 }}</ref>重建工程于2009年夏天完成，共耗资4700万美元。在此次翻修工程中，施工部门延长了车站站台和雨棚使得其可容纳12节编组的列车、增大了车站站房的面积，此外施工部门还在站台上还装有空调的候车亭并更新了导视系统<ref name="MetroparkStation">{{citation | last = Moss    | first = Adam   | title = Metropark Station   | publisher = Wikimedia Commons   | date = June 11, 2014   | url = https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Metropark_Station.jpg   | accessdate = December 12, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release      | title = CONSTRUCTION BEGINS ON A NEW METROPARK STATION    | publisher = New Jersey Transit   | date = April 23, 2007   | url = http://www.njtransit.com/tm/tm_servlet.srv?hdnPageAction=PressReleaseTo&PRESS_RELEASE_ID=2314   | accessdate = December 12, 2015}}</ref>。

===客流===
2001年以来，本站是新泽西运输除了位于市中心的枢纽车站外最繁忙的车站：车站于2006年平日每日客流超过7000人次，系第一个达到该数字的非市中心枢纽车站<ref name="njt boardings"/>。许多居住在[[史泰登岛|史泰登岛]]的居民也会利用本站或[[普林斯顿枢纽站|普林斯顿枢纽站]]前往[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]<ref name="njt boardings">{{cite web|url=https://webfiles.berkeley.edu/~lensovet/njtboardingdata.htm |title=New Jersey Transit rail boarding numbers 2007-1999 |work=Berkeley |accessdate=June 28, 2008 }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

==车站结构==
[[File:Metropark_Station.jpg|thumb]]
本站设有2座侧式月台，中间为四条股道，有[[东北走廊|东北走廊]]经过。美铁大部分中长途列车及部分新泽西通勤铁路快车使用中间两条股道通过车站，外侧两条股道有[[新泽西通勤铁路|新泽西通勤铁路]][[东北走廊线|东北走廊线]]列车和部分美铁中短途列车经停。由于美铁大部分列车在[[特伦顿公共交通中心|特伦顿]]和[[紐瓦克賓夕法尼亞車站|纽瓦克]]区间基本不停站，1986年本站东侧和西侧咽喉安装MENLO和ISELIN两座菱形道岔以方便美铁列车停靠车站而无需长时间借用外侧股道。
